# Instructions to setup

## Step 1
- Install RKE2 for windows (needs to have WSL installed first)

## Step 2
- Setup local storage folders.  
    - "C:\k8\local-storage\data1" and "C:\k8\local-storage\data2"

## Step 3
- Update the pv.yaml to use the correct node name
- Deploy different yaml files
    - $ kubectl apply -f storageclass.yaml
    - $ kubectl apply -f pv.yaml
    - $ kubectl apply -f pvc.yaml
    - $ kubectl apply -f stateful.yaml
    - $ kubectl apply -f service.yaml
- Or just deploy the folder as a whole
    - $ kubectl apply -f ../